data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Tuscany Woods in Oldsmar is a stunning residential gated community with much to offer. Built in 2016. With an open floorplan, vaulted ceilings, and a sliding glass door to your private patio this home is a fantastic space for entertaining. The interior wood cabinets, granite countertops, and tile floors are on the first floor. The property also includes three carpeted bedrooms, a walk-in closet in the master bedroom, and a dedicated laundry area upstairs for convenience. Don't forget the hurricane shutters and one-car garage.  Living in a community located on a preserve with amenities like trails, a splash park, and a recreation center all within a few hundred feet is a great advantage. HOA fees include a gated entrance, exterior maintenance, insurance, sewer, trash, and water. You'll have convenient access to outdoor activities and recreational facilities right at your doorstep. It's a fantastic opportunity to enjoy nature, stay active, and have fun with friends and family. Schedule your showing today.
